quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,48,is se pehlay bhi inn logon ne fitnah angazi ki koshishen ki hain aur tumhe nakaam karne ke liye yeh har terhan ki tdbiron ka ulat phair kar chuke hain yahan taq ke un ki marzi ke khilaaf haq aa gaya aur Allah ka kaam ho kar raha
9,49,"un mein se koi hai jo kehta hai ke"" mujhe rukhsat day degiye aur mujh ko ftne mein nah dalie"" sun rakho! ftne hi mein to yeh log parre hue hain aur jahannum ne un kafiroon ko ghair rakha hai"
9,50,tumhara bhala hota hai to inhen ranj hota hai aur tum par koi museebat aati hai to yeh mun phair kar khush khush palatne hain aur kehte jatay hain ke acha howa hum ne pehlay hi apna maamla theek kar liya tha
9,51,"un se kaho"" hamein hargiz koi ( buraiee ya bhalai ) nahi pahunchti magar woh jo Allah ne hamaray liye likh di hai Allah hi hamara Mooli hai, aur ahal imaan ko isi par bharosa karna chahiye """
9,52,"un se kaho,"" tum hamaray maamla mein jis cheez ke muntazir ho woh is ke siwa aur kya hai ke do bhulaiyon mein se aik bhalai hai aur hum tumahray maamla mein jis cheez ke muntazir hain woh yeh hai ke Allah khud tum ko saza deta hai ya hamaray hathon dlwata hai? acha to ab tum bhi intzaar karo aur hum bhi tumahray sath muntazir hain """
9,53,"un se kaho"" tum apne maal khuwa raazi khusi kharch karo ya ba-karahat, bahar haal woh qubool nah kiye jayen ge kyunkay tum fasik log ho """
9,54,"un ke diye hue maal qubool nah honay ki koi wajah is ke siwa nahi hai ke unhon ne Allah aur is ke rasool se kufar kya hai, namaz ke liye atay hain to kasmsakatay hue atay hain aur raah khuda mein kharch karte hain to baadal nakhwast_h kharch karte hain"
